snippet: When plans A and B failed to work on Thursday, Serena Williams resorted to pulling out 'Plan C' to keep alive her dreams of landing an elusive 22nd grand slam title at the French Open....
lead_paragraph: When plans A and B failed to work on Thursday, Serena Williams resorted to pulling out 'Plan C' to keep alive her dreams of landing an elusive 22nd grand slam title at the French Open.
